      "description": "The Kurv Yield Prem Stratgey Netflix ETF (NFLP) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in communication services equity. The fund seeks to provide current income and capped gains on the Netflix stock (NFLX) through a synthetic covered call strategy, collateralized by cash and short-term fixed-income instruments. The actively managed fund uses both standardized exchange-traded and FLEX options. NFLP was launched on Oct 27, 2023 and is issued by Kurv.",
